line_1: With bloated Toads, an odious Bearing, charg'd.
line_2: See his proud Standard o're his Tent enlarg'd!

line_1: With all the Monarch's Trophies charg'd:
line_2: And Thou, Imperial Windsor, stand inlarg'd,

line_1: And captious Science against Reason charg'd.
line_2: Ill grounded Maxims by false Gloss enlarg'd,

line_1: And brings at his return a bosom charged,
line_2: With rich instruction, and a soul enlarged.

line_1: The pleader rose with brief full charg'd,
line_2: And on the pris'ner's crimes enlarg'd —
